I still think you want to fade the inflation narrative at least through June (2022 peak rate of inflation).
If not for all of 2023.
Comps are easy breezy and expectations remain high (e.g. February consensus 6%; FOMC year-end dots at 4.4%). https://twitter.com/DeFiSurfer808/status/1632873657612525570 https://t.co/DJzzMQAd8U
